---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<Base
  title="Holiday Homes Palm Jumeirah 2026 — From AED 500/night"
  description="Find holiday homes on Palm Jumeirah from AED 500/night. Villas and apartments with private beach access. Best for families and luxury short stays."
>
<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal to-navy text-white py-12 px-4 text-center">
  <div class="text-sm text-green-200 mb-2">📍 Palm Jumeirah</div>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-3">Holiday Homes Palm Jumeirah — From AED 500/Night</h1>
  <p class="text-green-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Compare furnished villas and apartments on Palm Jumeirah. Private beach access. Skyline views. Perfect for families and special occasions.</p>
  <a href="/get-quotes?ref=palm-homes&type=home" class="bg-yellow-400 text-navy px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-black hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-colors inline-block">Find Palm Jumeirah Holiday Homes →</a>
</div>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy">Holiday Homes on Palm Jumeirah</h2>
    <p>Palm Jumeirah is Dubai's most iconic address and the most sought-after area for premium holiday homes. One-bedroom apartments in the trunk start from AED 500/night, while private villas on the fronds range from AED 2,000–8,000/night.</p>
    <p>Holiday homes on the Palm offer private beach access, resort-style pools, and views of the Dubai Marina skyline. The Nakheel Mall on the trunk provides shopping and dining, while Atlantis and The Royal at the crescent offer world-class restaurants and water parks.</p>
    <p>The Palm is best for families seeking space and privacy, couples celebrating special occasions, and groups who want a villa with multiple bedrooms. It is 20 minutes from Dubai Airport and connected by monorail to the mainland tram network.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <a href="/holiday-homes" class="text-teal font-semibold hover:underline">← Back to all holiday home areas</a>
  </div>
</div>
</Base>
